div.p:
Allow me to express my sincere congratulations, dear friend, on your elevation by your gracious Sovereign into his Council;



      M is probably referring to Regel's promotion to the rank of Wirklich Staatsrath [Effective Counsellor of State] in the Russian table of ranks.
 and let me hope that, with your robust good health, you may enjoy this new honour for a long time to come. I always admire your indefatigable activity, which is finding expression in so many directions.
